BOOM!                           
OH, WHAT'S THAT, STEVEN?        

187
00:17:14,801 --> 00:17:17,935
>> Steven: IT'S A TOGETHER      
BREAKFAST.                      
>> Amethyst: ALL RIGHT! SNACKS! 

188
00:17:17,937 --> 00:17:20,738
>> Steven: NO!                  
