[ GRUNTS ]                      
SKILLS!                         

197
00:18:09,689 --> 00:18:13,357
>> Amethyst: GET BACK HERE.     
>> Steven: YOU'RE COMPLETELY    
MISSING THE POINT OF THIS.      

198
00:18:13,359 --> 00:18:18,696
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]           
>> Amethyst: HEY, WAIT A SECOND.
>> Pearl: STEVEN!               

199
00:18:18,698 --> 00:18:21,966
THERE YOU ARE.                  
>> Steven: PEARL! SWEET!        
TWO OUT OF THREE.               

200
00:18:21,968 --> 00:18:27,972
>> Pearl: OH, OH!               
STEVEN, BE CAREFUL.             
>> Steven: WHY?                 

201
00:18:27,974 --> 00:18:31,542
WHA--?                          
[ GASPS ]                       
WHOA.                           

202
00:18:31,544 --> 00:18:34,412
[ PULSATING ]                   
>> Pearl: YOU REALLY SHOULDN'T  
BE IN HERE.                     

203
00:18:34,414 --> 00:18:38,416
THIS IS THE CRYSTAL HEART.      
OH!                             
IT'S CONNECTED TO THE MOST      

204
00:18:38,418 --> 00:18:46,090
DANGEROUS AREAS OF THE TEMPLE.  
HOLD ON TIGHT AND DON'T LOOK    
DOWN.                           

205
00:18:46,092 --> 00:18:53,831
>> Steven: HUH?                 
>> Pearl: OH!                   
>> Steven: [ SCREAMS ]          

206
00:18:53,833 --> 00:18:57,668
