[ SIZZLES ]                     
[ DISEMBODIED SCREAMING ]       

211
00:19:26,865 --> 00:19:30,134
>> PEARL: Steven, we're getting 
you out of here.                
>> AMETHYST: Come on.           

212
00:19:30,136 --> 00:19:33,137
>> Steven: HUH?                 
THIS IS GREAT!                  
WE'RE ALL TOGETHER.             

213
00:19:33,139 --> 00:19:36,807
>> Garnet: [ GASPS ]            
HUH?                            
>> Steven: WE CAN FINALLY EAT.  

214
