[ RUMBLING ]                    
[ DISEMBODIED YELLING ]         

217
00:19:50,156 --> 00:19:54,659
>> Steven: WHOA!                
>> Garnet: IT'S TRYING TO       
ESCAPE.                         

218
00:19:54,661 --> 00:19:56,227
