219
00:19:59,831 --> 00:20:01,699
>> Amethyst: GET BACK!          

220
00:20:08,073 --> 00:20:13,044
>> All: STEVEN!                 
>> Steven: [ MOANS ]            

221
00:20:16,181 --> 00:20:23,854
TOGETHER BREAKFAST?             
[ SCREAMS ]                     
>> Pearl: IT'S TAKEN REFUGE IN  

222
