>> Pearl: AAH! IT'S HORRIBLE!   

224
00:20:39,371 --> 00:20:44,609
>> Steven: I DIDN'T WANT THIS.  
I JUST WANTED TO EAT TOGETHER   
LIKE -- LIKE BEST BUDS.         

225
00:20:44,611 --> 00:20:48,379
[ GROANING ]                    
>> Garnet: STEVEN, YOU'VE GOT TO
GET AWAY.                       

226
00:20:48,381 --> 00:20:58,889
>> Steven: BUT MY BREAKFAST.    
THAT'S ENOUGH!                  
[ Straining ] I DON'T CARE IF   

227
00:20:58,891 --> 00:21:07,565
YOU...ARE THE MOST IMPORTANT    
MEAL OF THE DAY.                
[ GRUNTING ]                    

228
00:21:07,567 --> 00:21:12,803
I MADE YOU TO BRING US TOGETHER,
NOT TO TEAR US APART!           

229
00:21:20,379 --> 00:21:28,953
[ PANTING ]                     
I'M SORRY, GUYS.                
I GUESS I DREAMED TOO BIG.      

230
00:21:47,739 --> 00:21:52,910
>> Steven: IT LOOKS GREAT.      
